Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.26,0:17:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我可以  我肯定会帮你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I'd help you if I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.88,0:17:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我会的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You know I would.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.22,0:17:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,把狗还给我  放我走吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Just give me Dog, let me go,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.01,0:17:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你再也不会见到我了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}you'll never see me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.14,0:17:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是你想要的吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Is that what you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.28,0:17:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.08,0:17:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,找到博西了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Found Bossie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.16,0:17:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,特纳呢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And Turner?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.43,0:18:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我努力过了  但没能救他\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I tried. I couldn't save him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.81,0:18:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,-我努力过了  -没关系  孩子\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- I tried. - It's okay, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.85,0:18:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你做了正确的事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You did the right thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.73,0:18:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你把他带回家了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You brought him home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.07,0:19:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,主啊  我们把兄弟特纳交给你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Lord, we release our brother Turner to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.57,0:19:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,请您拥紧他\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Please, hold him close.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.35,0:19:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,以主之名  阿门\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}In your name, oh Lord, amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.15,0:19:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,阿门\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.00,0:20:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝在此\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}God is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.55,0:20:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他很愤怒\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}He's angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.56,0:20:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我很愤怒\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I'm angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.02,0:20:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你们感受到了吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Do you feel that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.40,0:20:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,去让他们感受到我们的怒火\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Go make them feel our wrath.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.00,0:21:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.42,0:21:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我有一个兄弟死了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}One of my brothers is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.80,0:21:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,他叫迈克尔·特纳\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Michael Turner was his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.97,0:21:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我们曾在世界各地并肩战斗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We fought all over the world together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.85,0:21:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我们最后一次驻扎回来后  教皇将他纳入麾下\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Pope brought him in after our last tour,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.06,0:21:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那时他刚创办公司\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}when he started his company.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.52,0:21:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为你们是士兵\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I thought you were soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.61,0:21:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我们曾经是\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We were.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.19,0:21:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,之后私营化了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Then we went private.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.24,0:21:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你之前没告诉过我你是佣兵\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You didn't tell me you were a merc.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.90,0:21:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这重要吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Mm, does it matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.03,0:21:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,都是一样的工作\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I mean, it's the same damn job.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.04,0:21:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,只是我们真能付得起生活费了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Except we could actually pay our bills.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.71,0:22:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,迈克尔跟我很像  他也没有家人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Michael was like me, you know? He didn't have a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.22,0:22:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,他就是我没能拥有的弟弟\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}He was the little brother I never had.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.47,0:22:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直想要的弟弟\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You know, the little brother I always wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.31,0:22:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,现在他死了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And he's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.73,0:22:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在这里失去过很多同伴\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You know, we lost a lot of people...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.15,0:22:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,一直很艰难\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}here, and it's been hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.61,0:22:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,但这次不一样\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Not like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.15,0:22:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}This is the first time
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.07,0:22:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,很长时间以来第一次失去了亲近的人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I've lost someone close to me in a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.16,0:22:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.58,0:22:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,或许除了你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}except maybe for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.34,0:22:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你那时并没失去我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You didn't lose me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.55,0:22:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我回去找过你  但你走了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I came back and you were gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.47,0:22:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你离开了我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You left me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.39,0:23:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我问你你想要什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I asked you what you wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.10,0:23:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你就走了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You left.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.90,0:23:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我害怕了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I got scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.24,0:23:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,怕什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.53,0:23:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,放手\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Letting go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.47,0:23:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,无所谓了  反正我们也不会有结果\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It doesn't matter. It wouldn't have worked anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.56,0:23:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能拥有幸福\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Couldn't have been happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.02,0:23:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,在这样一个世界里不可能\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Not in a world like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.73,0:23:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你的想法还是你家人的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Is that you talking or your family?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.52,0:23:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,难道你就没做过坏事吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Like you've never done things?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.03,0:23:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,杀人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Killed people.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.99,0:23:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你做过什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I know the things you've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.61,0:23:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你没权利指责我  根本没有\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You have no right to judge, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.95,0:24:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是真正的我  达里尔\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}This is me, Daryl.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.66,0:24:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不论是好的还是坏的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}The good and the bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.25,0:24:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,全都是我  一直如此\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}All of it. It always has been.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.71,0:24:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我不相信\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I don't believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.76,0:24:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那我也没办法\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Well, I can't help with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.26,0:24:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,但我可以帮你救自己\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}But I can help you save yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.68,0:24:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,因为不管怎样  我仍在乎你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Because despite everything, I still care about you,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.69,0:24:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我不希望你发生不好的事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}and I don't want anything bad to happen to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.78,0:24:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你必须交代点什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}So, you need to tell me something.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.57,0:24:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,任何事都行\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.11,0:24:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你不说  我就控制不了我的指挥官\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}'Cause if you can't, I can't control my commander
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.12,0:24:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,以及他的下一步行动\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}or what he will do next.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.45,0:24:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,特纳的死令他愤怒不已\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}He's angry about Turner,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.79,0:24:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,他要找人付出代价\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}and he wants someone to pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.26,0:24:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,有个女人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}There's a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.76,0:25:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,她是首领\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}She's the leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.39,0:25:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他们用暗语交流  因为我是外人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}They were speaking in code 'cause I was an outsider.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.65,0:25:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,有一个高瘦的男人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}There was a tall, skinny guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.73,0:25:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是个话痨\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Never shuts up.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.57,0:25:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,还有个背着猎枪的神父\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And a priest who carries a shotgun.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.36,0:25:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,那是他们的领导层吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}That's their leadership?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.86,0:25:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  但他们有人数优势\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Yeah. But they have the numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.08,0:25:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,其中一个士兵说漏嘴了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And one of their soldiers slipped up,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.49,0:25:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,他要去找他们那三十几个战士\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}and he was gonna go meet three dozen of their fighters.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.66,0:25:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,比你这里的十五个士兵多得多\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}That's way more than the 15 you got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.37,0:25:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,看来你被关在这也没闲着\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Well, you've been doing your work down here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.39,0:25:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我今晚会叫人把你放出来\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I'll have you moved out of here tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.22,0:25:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,这样你能舒服些\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}so you can be more comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.94,0:25:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我何时能见到他\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}When do I meet him?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.86,0:25:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,教皇\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}This Pope?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.82,0:26:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,快了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.18,0:26:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你说得对\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Well, you were right.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.85,0:26:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,他很难降服\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}He was hard to break.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.06,0:26:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,他告诉我  敌人比我们想象中要多得多\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}He told me there are a lot more out there than we thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.48,0:26:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,比我们这里的人数多两倍以上\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}More than twice the force we have in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.36,0:26:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为他适合这里\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I think he'll be good here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.24,0:26:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我们需要人手\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And we need the manpower,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.37,0:26:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,特纳死了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}with Turner gone
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.54,0:26:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,尼科尔斯和蒙塔尼奥仍下落不明\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}and Nicholls and Montanio still missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.72,0:27:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,说句话\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.47,0:27:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道我讨厌你这样做\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You know I hate it when you do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.51,0:27:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,做什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Do what?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.60,0:27:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,晾着我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Freeze me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.93,0:27:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,一切不是围着你转的  莉娅\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Not everything is about you, Leah.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.86,0:27:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我从没这样说过\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I never said it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.19,0:27:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Oh, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.69,0:27:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我们在这里\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}'Cause here we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.61,0:27:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,浪费了一天追踪敌人的时间  只因为你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Losing a day of tracking our enemy 'cause you --
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.03,0:27:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你要对老男友进行希望渺茫的审问\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}you had to go on a fishing expedition with an old boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.19,0:27:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,继续吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}So, go on, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.48,0:27:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.44,0:28:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你查到想查的事了吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You find what you're looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.28,0:28:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我说过他有用  我说对了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I told you he would be useful, and I was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.74,0:28:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,他很像我们\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}He's a lot like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.75,0:28:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,他不怕痛苦  他不怕死亡\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Pain doesn't scare him, death doesn't scare him.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.92,0:28:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,卡弗看到了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Carver saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.25,0:28:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托  你也看到了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Come on, you see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.42,0:28:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我只看到了一个想上你的男人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I just see a guy who wants to get in your pants.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.01,0:28:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.89,0:28:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.85,0:28:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他是忍不住盯着他所爱过的人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Who couldn't stop gazing at somebody he loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.27,0:28:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我没说过他爱过我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I never said he loved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.15,0:28:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你今天本可以在外面杀了他\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You could've ended him out there today,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.95,0:28:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,而你没下手\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}and you didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.99,0:28:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.78,0:28:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,他曾对我有所意义\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}At one point, he meant something to me, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.87,0:28:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我对此没有隐瞒\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I've been open about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.42,0:29:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,但在你找到了我  我选择了这个大家庭的那天\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}But it ended the day you found me
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.21,0:29:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这一切就结束了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}and I chose this family,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.71,0:29:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我从没有后悔过做出那个决定\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}and I have never once regretted that decision,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.76,0:29:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不希望你后悔\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}and I don't want you to, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.05,0:29:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你后悔吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.57,0:29:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我更相信你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.82,0:29:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,相比其他人来说\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}More than the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.54,0:29:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.54,0:29:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得我们可以信任他吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You think we can trust him?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.00,0:29:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,可以\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.80,0:29:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.55,0:29:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,让我亲眼看看\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Now, let me see for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.47,0:29:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,有话要说吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You got something to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.27,0:30:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,说吧  别害羞\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Come on, man. Don't be shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.77,0:30:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你就要见老大了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You're about to meet the man.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.19,0:30:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这怂样留给你女友吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Yeah, save that coy shit for your girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.11,0:30:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,肖才不是谁的女友\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Aww, Shaw ain't nobody's girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.53,0:30:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我敢打赌这小子什么都听她的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I'm betting she wears the pants with homeboy here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.61,0:30:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你说是不是\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.12,0:30:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你屁都不懂  卡弗  闭嘴吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You don't know shit about shit, Carver. Knock it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.50,0:30:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,那我还是出去吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I guess I'll just show my dumb ass out, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.34,0:30:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,教皇快来了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Pope is on his way.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.47,0:30:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,在我见他之前  你想提醒我什么吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Anything you wanna tell me about this guy before I meet him?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.47,0:30:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,看我眼色行事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Just follow my lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.22,0:31:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,给  拿着\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Here! Take it! Take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.82,0:31:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,用这个\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Here! Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.64,0:32:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,快\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.53,0:33:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,由火铸就\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Forged by fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.33,0:33:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,由神指定\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Ordained by God.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.29,0:33:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎他\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Welcome him!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.21,0:33:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,赴汤蹈火\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Fortitudo Saludis!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.21,0:33:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}出自《圣经》拉丁语版钦定本诗篇140:8\N指上帝在争战之中赐予我勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.51,0:33:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你信上帝吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You believe in God?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.31,0:33:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不信\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}No. No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.02,0:33:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不再信了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.02,0:33:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在只信自己\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Guess I just believe in me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.07,0:33:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,这是个错误\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Well, that's a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.61,0:33:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,-为何  -因为你不是上帝\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- Why's that? - 'Cause you're not Him.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.45,0:33:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我通过了你的小测试\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I passed your little test, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.66,0:33:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,无论你怎么称呼那事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Whatever you want to call it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.99,0:33:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你以为这就结束了吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Oh, and you think that's the end of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.75,0:33:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你还想要我做什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}What else do you want from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.67,0:33:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I want...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.92,0:33:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要你理解\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I want you to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.52,0:34:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,坐\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.48,0:34:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都是在死亡谷认识的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We all met in the Valley of Death.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.82,0:34:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,反正我们是这样称呼那里的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}That's what we call it, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.66,0:34:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,阿富汗的山区\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Hills of Afghanistan.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.24,0:34:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我们为国奋战\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We fought for our country,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.33,0:34:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,把阵亡的战友抬下战场\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}carried our fallen brothers off the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.37,0:34:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,抬了太多人  后来我们都数不清了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Carried so many, we lost count after a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.42,0:34:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,政客们\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Politicians.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.38,0:34:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,只管开支票\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}They wrote the checks.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.47,0:34:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,根本不在乎我们\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We weren't anything to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.35,0:34:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我们只是道具\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Just props.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.39,0:34:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,下次竞选所用的道具\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Props for their next campaign.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.81,0:34:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,他们喜欢谈论上帝\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}See, they -- they talked about God.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.94,0:34:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不认识上帝\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}They didn't know God.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.15,0:34:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,他们没见过他的脸\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}They never saw His face.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.19,0:35:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不像我们\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It's not like we did.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.24,0:35:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我们看到上帝无处不在\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We saw God everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.41,0:35:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,他在鲜血  恐怖和死亡之中\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}He was in the blood and the horror and death.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.41,0:35:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,他在那  为我们指引方向\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}He was there, telling us where to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.25,0:35:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,在那段日子里  我们唯有指望他\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Didn't have much else to hold on to in those days but Him.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.51,0:35:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,还有彼此\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.97,0:35:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你抽烟吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You smoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.32,0:35:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那场战争差点永远废了我们\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}That war damn near ruined all of us for good.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.62,0:35:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,回国之后  我的部下都有永久性损伤\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Came home and my guys had permanent injuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.41,0:35:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,他们睡不着觉  找不到正经工作\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}They couldn't sleep. They couldn't find real jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.13,0:36:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,所以\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}So...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.63,0:36:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我们成了人们口中的佣兵\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}people called us mercenaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.68,0:36:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那些没人想做的脏活累活\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We did all the ugly, dirty work
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.14,0:36:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,都由我们来做\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}nobody else wanted to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.31,0:36:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,还拿到了丰厚的佣金\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Got paid for it, too. Handsomely.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.36,0:36:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,真正的脏活是在沦陷之后开始的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}The real dirty work started after the Fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.91,0:36:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我从没有经历过那样的战争\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Never been in a war like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.00,0:36:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,从没有见过那样的混乱\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Never seen that kind of chaos,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.54,0:36:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,而我以前什么都见过\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}and I had seen everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.17,0:36:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,但这个\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}But this...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.68,0:36:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我们做的那些事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Oh, the things we did.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.52,0:36:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,所有的死亡  日复一日\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}All that death, day after day after day...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.52,0:37:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不久以后  我和你有了同样的想法\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}After a while, I started to feel like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.82,0:37:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我在想  上帝哪去了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Wondering -- Wondering where God was.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.70,0:37:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,直到他再次现身\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Until He showed His face again.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.87,0:37:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,政客们  还有最后一场仗要打\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}See, politicians -- they had one last war to get behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.42,0:37:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这一次  敌人是我们\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}This time, coming for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.46,0:37:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,炸弹如暴雨般落下\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}The bombs came thick and fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.34,0:37:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,一直没有停\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It did not stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.43,0:37:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我们和一些战友走散了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We lost some of our own,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.56,0:37:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不得不穿越大火去救他们\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}had to run through the fire to save them.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.19,0:37:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在城镇边缘找到了一座小教堂\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Found this little church at the edge of town,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.48,0:37:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我们躲在那里  看着一切\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}and we holed up there as everything --
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.19,0:37:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说所有的一切  在身边燃烧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}and I mean everything -- burned around us.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.91,0:37:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,等火终于熄灭了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}When the fires finally died down,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.58,0:37:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我看向我的部下\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I looked at my people...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.71,0:38:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我简直不敢相信\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I could not believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.13,0:38:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,没留一滴血\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Not a trace of blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.38,0:38:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,没有烧伤\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}No burn marks.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.22,0:38:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,连擦伤都没有\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Not even a scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.76,0:38:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那时我就知道了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And that's when I knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.35,0:38:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是天选之人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We were the Chosen Ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.15,0:38:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这些人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}These men --
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.19,0:38:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,火焰伤不了这些人的身躯\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}These men upon whose bodies the fire had no power.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.08,0:38:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝今晚选中了你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}God chose you tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.17,0:38:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你毫发无伤  活着逃出了火场\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I mean, you -- you came out of that fire alive and whole.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.01,0:38:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,看看你  现在坐在这里\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And look at you now, sitting right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.47,0:38:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你受伤了吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.14,0:38:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,被烧到了吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Any burns?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.47,0:38:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,有擦伤吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}A scratch?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.10,0:39:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我以前经历过更糟的事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I've been through worse before.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.99,0:39:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你饿吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Are. You. Hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.07,0:39:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你说得对\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You were right.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.11,0:39:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,关于这家伙\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}About this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.44,0:39:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我当然对了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Of course I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.28,0:39:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,分他点  博西\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Give him some, Bossie.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.20,0:40:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,别太贪\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Don't be greedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.83,0:40:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,他现在是家人了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}He's family now.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.59,0:40:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道他做了什么吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You know what he did, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.47,0:40:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,他背着死去的兄弟走了10英里\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}He walked 10 miles with his dead brother on his back.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.60,0:40:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,10英里\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}10 miles.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.64,0:40:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,这需要多大的力量啊\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}The strength that took...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.48,0:40:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我们有多感激吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You have any idea how grateful we are?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.15,0:40:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,特纳会有一个体面的葬礼\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Turner will have a proper burial.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.57,0:40:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是做了我们都会做的事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Just did what any one of us would've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.50,0:40:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,还疼吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}These still hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.09,0:40:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,需要什么吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You need anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.05,0:41:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我只想问一个问题\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I just have one question.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.10,0:41:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}S-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.48,0:41:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,有件事我一直很困惑\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Something's been bothering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.06,0:41:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你的伤口\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Your wounds...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.61,0:41:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,在背上\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}are on your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.82,0:41:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,教皇  今天已经够辛苦了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Pope, it's been a rough day.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.90,0:41:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想弄清楚  肖\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Just getting clarity, Shaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.03,0:41:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,特纳被袭击时  你在哪里\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Where were you when Turner was being attacked?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.04,0:41:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我在现场  我给你说过了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I-I was right there, just like I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.08,0:41:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,面朝敌人吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Facing the enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.42,0:41:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.42,0:41:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他受的苦够多了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}He's been through enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.97,0:41:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,害怕了会跑是人的本能反应\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Human nature is to run when you are scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.23,0:41:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你懂的吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You know what that's like, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.57,0:42:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,直面恐惧需要非凡的勇气\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It takes divine strength to face your fear head-on.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.28,0:42:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,为别人赌上一切\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Risk everything for someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.04,0:42:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都看到了你所做的事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We all saw what you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.66,0:42:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,先把肖救出火场  你也感受到了吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Getting Shaw out of the fire first, and you felt it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.75,0:42:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,为了保护你  他愿意做到什么地步\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}How far he would go just to keep you safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.97,0:42:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,今天  上帝用火洗礼了你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Today, God baptized you in that fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.76,0:42:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,让你成了我们的一员\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Made you one of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.94,0:42:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不过\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You see...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.40,0:42:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我忘了告诉你一件事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}there's one thing I forgot to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.11,0:42:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,永远不要背弃你的兄弟\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Never turn your back on your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.33,0:42:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝不只用火来洗礼\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}God doesn't only use fire as His baptism.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.83,0:42:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,他也用火来表达愤怒\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It's also His wrath.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.99,0:43:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是天选之人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We are the Chosen Ones!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.95,0:43:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我们奔向战场\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We run into the battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.58,0:43:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我们奔入火场\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We run into the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.59,0:43:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,永远如此\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Always.

